'''ZC45病毒'''（SL-CoV ZC45）與'''ZXC21病毒'''（SL-CoV ZXC21），被部分媒體稱為'''舟山蝙蝠病毒'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-52133480|title=肺炎疫情：新冠病毒到底哪來的？科學界的幾種說法|author=林祖偉|publisher=BBC中文|date=2020-04-03|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730134005/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-52133480|dead-url=no}}</ref>，皆為[[嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症相關冠狀病毒|嚴重急性呼吸系統綜合症相關冠狀病毒]]（SARSr-CoV）的病毒株，在中國[[浙江|浙江]][[舟山|舟山]]的[[小菊頭蝠|小菊頭蝠]]樣本中發現，於2018年發表。這兩個病毒株屬於[[严重急性呼吸系统综合征冠状病毒2|SARS-CoV-2]]的演化支<ref name="JiangDu2020">{{cite journal|last1=Jiang|first1=Shibo|last2=Du|first2=Lanying|last3=Shi|first3=Zhengli|title=An emerging coronavirus causing pneumonia outbreak in Wuhan, China: calling for developing therapeutic and prophylactic strategies|journal=Emerging Microbes & Infections|volume=9|issue=1|year=2020|pages=275–277|issn=2222-1751|doi=10.1080/22221751.2020.1723441}}</ref>，全[[基因組|基因組]]核酸序列與SARS-CoV-2的相似度約為88%<ref name="LauLuk2020">{{cite journal|last1=Lau|first1=Susanna K.P.|last2=Luk|first2=Hayes K.H.|last3=Wong|first3=Antonio C.P.|last4=Li|first4=Kenneth S.M.|last5=Zhu|first5=Longchao|last6=He|first6=Zirong|last7=Fung|first7=Joshua|last8=Chan|first8=Tony T.Y.|last9=Fung|first9=Kitty S.C.|last10=Woo|first10=Patrick C.Y.|title=Possible Bat Origin of Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|volume=26|issue=7|year=2020|pages=1542–1547|issn=1080-6040|doi=10.3201/eid2607.200092}}</ref><ref name="ZhouChen2020">{{cite journal|last1=Zhou|first1=Hong|last2=Chen|first2=Xing|last3=Hu|first3=Tao|last4=Li|first4=Juan|last5=Song|first5=Hao|last6=Liu|first6=Yanran|last7=Wang|first7=Peihan|last8=Liu|first8=Di|last9=Yang|first9=Jing|last10=Holmes|first10=Edward C.|last11=Hughes|first11=Alice C.|last12=Bi|first12=Yuhai|last13=Shi|first13=Weifeng|title=A Novel Bat Coronavirus Closely Related to SARS-CoV-2 Contains Natural Insertions at the S1/S2 Cleavage Site of the Spike Protein|journal=Current Biology|volume=30|issue=11|year=2020|pages=2196–2203.e3|issn=09609822|doi=10.1016/j.cub.2020.05.023}}</ref>，與[[严重急性呼吸道综合征冠状病毒|SARS-CoV]]的相似度則約為81%<ref name="HuZhu2018">{{cite journal|last1=Hu|first1=Dan|last2=Zhu|first2=Changqiang|last3=Ai|first3=Lele|last4=He|first4=Ting|last5=Wang|first5=Yi|last6=Ye|first6=Fuqiang|last7=Yang|first7=Lu|last8=Ding|first8=Chenxi|last9=Zhu|first9=Xuhui|last10=Lv|first10=Ruicheng|last11=Zhu|first11=Jin|last12=Hassan|first12=Bachar|last13=Feng|first13=Youjun|last14=Tan|first14=Weilong|last15=Wang|first15=Changjun|title=Genomic characterization and infectivity of a novel SARS-like coronavirus in Chinese bats|journal=Emerging Microbes & Infections|volume=7|issue=1|year=2018|pages=1–10|issn=2222-1751|doi=10.1038/s41426-018-0155-5}}</ref>。

==發現==
2015年至2017年間，研究人員在浙江[[舟山|舟山]]採集334隻[[小菊頭蝠|小菊頭蝠]]樣本，發現其中含有多種冠狀病毒序列，其中有兩個新病毒株（即ZC45與ZXC21）的[[基因組|基因組]]被完整定序，分別長29802與29732[[核鹼基|nt]]，彼此基因組序列相似度為97%。這兩個病毒株的基因組序列與[[严重急性呼吸道综合征冠状病毒|SARS-CoV]]相似度約為81%，刺突蛋白（S）胺基酸序列和SARS-CoV的相似度則為77%，皆低於[[WIV病毒|Rs3367]]等數種較早發現的蝙蝠SARSr-CoV和SARS-CoV的相似度，且兩病毒刺突蛋白的S1次單元胺基酸序列和其他蝙蝠SARSr-CoV差異較大，與其相似度最高者（Rs806）亦僅有83%。動物實驗顯示ZC45病毒可感染[[實驗大鼠|實驗大鼠]]，在多個器官造成發炎，其中以[[腦|腦]]組織最為明顯<ref name="HuZhu2018"/>。

==與SARS-CoV-2的相似==
2020年1月，[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]甫爆發後，研究人員定序[[严重急性呼吸系统综合征冠状病毒2|SARS-CoV-2]]的基因組，發現ZC45與ZXC21是當時已知核酸序列與SARS-CoV-2相似度最高的病毒，約有88%{{Notetag|1=但後來發表的[[RaTG13病毒|RaTG13病毒]]、[[RmYN02病毒|RmYN02病毒]]等基因組與SARS-CoV-2的相似度更高，分別為96.2%與93.3%<ref name="ZhouChen2020"/>。}}，高於SARS-CoV-2與SARS-CoV相似度的82%<ref name="JiangDu2020"/>，共同組成一[[演化支|演化支]]，不過兩病毒與與SARS-CoV-2在刺突蛋白的相似度較低，核酸序列的相似度約為75%，其中在S2次單元的相似度比S1次單元的高許多，在位於S1末端、與宿主細胞受體結合的[[受體結合結構域|受體結合結構域]]（receptor binding domain, RBD）相似度僅約60%，低於SARS-CoV-2與SARS-CoV在此的相似度（約74%）<ref name="ZhouChen2020"/><ref name="LuZhao2020">{{cite journal|last1=Lu|first1=Roujian|last2=Zhao|first2=Xiang|last3=Li|first3=Juan|last4=Niu|first4=Peihua|last5=Yang|first5=Bo|last6=Wu|first6=Honglong|last7=Wang|first7=Wenling|last8=Song|first8=Hao|last9=Huang|first9=Baoying|last10=Zhu|first10=Na|last11=Bi|first11=Yuhai|last12=Ma|first12=Xuejun|last13=Zhan|first13=Faxian|last14=Wang|first14=Liang|last15=Hu|first15=Tao|last16=Zhou|first16=Hong|last17=Hu|first17=Zhenhong|last18=Zhou|first18=Weimin|last19=Zhao|first19=Li|last20=Chen|first20=Jing|last21=Meng|first21=Yao|last22=Wang|first22=Ji|last23=Lin|first23=Yang|last24=Yuan|first24=Jianying|last25=Xie|first25=Zhihao|last26=Ma|first26=Jinmin|last27=Liu|first27=William J|last28=Wang|first28=Dayan|last29=Xu|first29=Wenbo|last30=Holmes|first30=Edward C|last31=Gao|first31=George F|last32=Wu|first32=Guizhen|last33=Chen|first33=Weijun|last34=Shi|first34=Weifeng|last35=Tan|first35=Wenjie|title=Genomic characterisation and epidemiology of 2019 novel coronavirus: implications for virus origins and receptor binding|journal=The Lancet|volume=395|issue=10224|year=2020|pages=565–574|issn=01406736|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(20)30251-8}}</ref>。

===爭議===
{{main|閆麗夢#指控中華人民共和國政府隱瞞2019冠状病毒病疫情事件}}
2020年9月，前[[香港大學|香港大學]]病毒學研究員[[閆麗夢|閆麗夢]]在美國發表未經[[同行評審|同行評審]]的論文，指控SARS-CoV-2並非自然產生，而是在實驗室經改造ZC45與ZXC21（或稱「舟山蝙蝠病毒」）而成的人造病毒，論文指出SARS-CoV-2基因組中的許多特徵不見於其他冠狀病毒，且ZC45與ZXC21的序列和其「十分相似」，很可能是製作SARS-CoV-2的來源模板，而與SARS-CoV-2關係接近、但在疫情爆發後才發表的[[RaTG13病毒|RaTG13病毒]]、[[RmYN02病毒|RmYN02病毒]]與[[穿山甲冠狀病毒|穿山甲冠狀病毒]]可能為虛構<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zenodo.org/record/4028830#.YAfJUy2z1N0|title=Unusual Features of the SARS-CoV-2 Genome Suggesting Sophisticated Laboratory Modification Rather Than Natural Evolution and Delineation of Its Probable Synthetic Route|author=Yan, Li-Meng; Kang, Shu; Guan, Jie; Hu, Shanchang|publisher=Rule of Law Society & Rule of Law Foundation|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915012013/https://zenodo.org/record/4028830#.YAfJUy2z1N0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4009390|title=Virologist releases paper claiming coronavirus made in Chinese lab|author=Keoni Everington|date=2020-09-15|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115024537/https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4009390|dead-url=no|publisher=[[英文台灣日報|Taiwan News]]}}</ref>。此論文的可信度受到諸多學者批評<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/13/technology/another-unfounded-study-on-origins-of-virus-spreads-online.html?searchResultPosition=1|title=Another ‘Unfounded’ Study on Origins of Virus Spreads Online|author=Katherine J. Wu|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102053613/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/10/13/technology/another-unfounded-study-on-origins-of-virus-spreads-online.html?searchResultPosition=1|dead-url=no|publisher=The New York Times}}</ref>，許多病毒學家表示ZC45與ZXC21和SARS-CoV-2的序列差異大於10%，約有3500個[[核鹼基|鹼基]]不同，差異已大到幾乎不可能為人工製造<ref name="nationalgeographic">{{cite web |url=https://www.nationalgeographic.com/science/2020/09/coronavirus-origins-misinformation-yan-report-fact-check-cvd/ |title=Why misinformation about COVID-19's origins keeps going viral: Another piece of coronavirus misinformation is making the rounds. Here's how to sift through the muck. |first1=Monique |last1=Brouillette |first2=Rebecca |last2=Renner |date=2020-09-18 |publisher=[[National_Geographic|National Geographic]] |accessdate=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924083921/https://www.nationalgeographic.com/science/2020/09/coronavirus-origins-misinformation-yan-report-fact-check-cvd/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有學者並形容此論文為[[垃圾科學|垃圾科學]]<ref name="CNN_Kuzniaetal_20201021">{{Cite news| last1 = Kuznia| first1 = Rob| last2 = Bronstein| first2 = Scott| last3 = Griffin| first3 = Drew| last4 = Devine| first4 = Curt| title = How a Covid-19 origin theory backed by Bannon unraveled - CNNPolitics| work = CNN| access-date = 2020-10-22| date = 2020-10-21| url = https://edition.cnn.com/2020/10/21/politics/coronavirus-lab-theory-yan-bannon-invs/index.html| archive-date = 2022-05-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220503181006/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/10/21/politics/coronavirus-lab-theory-yan-bannon-invs/index.html}}</ref>。

